Package: patientSimOrchestrate
Type: Package
Title: Multi-model orchestration for patientSim bundles
Version: 1.3.0
Author: Jarrod Dalton [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jarrod Dalton <daltonj@ccf.org>
Authors@R: person(given = "Jarrod",
                  family = "Dalton",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "daltonj@ccf.org")
Description: Add-on orchestration utilities for the patientSim ecosystem. Provides an
    orchestration bundle wrapper that composes multiple ModelBundles on a
    shared patient timeline, supports policy-based eligibility, deterministic
    event precedence via process_id rewriting, and optional episode/care-
    context transitions implemented as ordinary state updates.
License: Proprietary
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: patientSimCore, R6
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
